        <section id="privacy-policy" class="w-9/12 mx-auto">
            <h1 class="text-center">Privacy Policy</h1>
            <small>Last Updated: April 2nd, 2024</small>
            <ol class="mt-8">
                <li class="pb-4">
                    <b>Personal Information</b><br />
                    We may collect personal information from users in various ways,
                    including but not limited to when users fill out forms on our
                    site, subscribe to our newsletter, or engage in other activities,
                    services, features, or resources we make available on our website.
                    The personal information we may collect includes First Name,
                    Last Name, Email Address, Phone Number, Message, and Interested
