                    <b>Data Retention</b><br />
                    Data collected through our website is retained on Chisme indefinitely
                    unless we receive a deletion request. However, data on third-party
                    sites such as Facebook, Google Analytics, and TikTok is not retained
                    for longer than 18 months.
                </li>
                <li class="pb-4">
                    <b>Third-Party Sharing</b><br />
                    We do not share user data with any third-party services or entities
                    outside of the tracking pixels mentioned and our CRM platform,
                    Chisme.
                </li>
                <li class="pb-4">
