                    If you wish to have your data deleted from our records, please
                    send an email to Julia Kuttler (julia@rootsofpossibility.com)
                    with the subject line “Data Deletion Request” and provide your
                    information so that we can process your request.

                    <li class="pb-4">
                        <b>Age Restrictions</b><br />
                        While there are no age restrictions for accessing our website,
                        our services are only provided to adults aged 18 years or
                        older, and minors with a parent or guardian’s consent.
                    </li>
                    <li class="pb-4">
                        <b>Privacy Policy Updates</b><br />
                        We reserve the right to update our Privacy Policy as needed.
                        It is your responsibility to regularly review this policy
                        for any changes. By continuing to use our website, you agree
                        to the updated terms.
                    </li>
                    <li class="pb-4">
                        <b>International Data Transfers</b><br />
                        Our website is not intentionally targeting users in specific
                        geographical areas, and there are no intentional data transfers
